{"tid":1191833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日行你就行，咪搞咁多野","createTime":"2019-06-08T06:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T05:03:38.000Z","uid":222907,"like":34,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b3ade8f5e970b841dac00913972c44c3f51b8d","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"有事起上黎<br />\n<br />\n留案底，比律政司告，請律師，交堂費<br />\n<br />\n返工還債，破產?<br />\n<br />\n無野輸?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔諗下你屋企人既? 你將來呢?<br />\n<br />\n你以為你會被寫入歷史? 安家費都無啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd98fac3fa6ed4eeb37d806c825059be4cae0f7d","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":11,"dislike":12,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"連登良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9ddaa0e669c87cc143ecc7b5e62b067c88b7bd","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":12,"dislike":18,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"太多無恥之徒教唆小朋友做犯法嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要將佢英雄化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa5e608839333e5f04837c0589522c18be050f1","tid":1191833,"uid":31749,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7afd137b6774766c508e17d86327e3c44a74a9a5","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"負皮d 人無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e7b3196258a0a5137d713cca88d7dbfe8c2162","tid":1191833,"uid":124983,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:05:17.000Z","msg":"有版你睇<br />\n黃台要走佬 天琦同一眾坐幾碌<br />\n但政權依家不倒 所有野都無變<br />\n你要重覆佢地既路你既事<br />\n吹到係革命契機你咪衝囉<br />\n你驚人篤灰你就自己離隊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99299951f2fa2ddbaff8f7b2e5989e0239afe08","tid":1191833,"uid":135867,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"點解一入來成個post吉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528304d4f78099dd9295536eb592dc6df24f4737","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42da924dada921e93a6ff5fb864de0874d9e74e4","tid":1191833,"uid":2383,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/atvGTrP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatvGTrP.png&h=4c34d254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c89e5eed303acc560e91ad7ccd5e566fb7e2d8","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:04:32.000Z","msg":"連登良心推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f3c8c1996aeef6989539d06a48e05f4395e66f","tid":1191833,"uid":196864,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:10:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>共同目標 都有一百種表達方式<br />\n有心人 自會用自己方式去支援<br />\n<br />\n記住 不批鬥 不內亂 不受煽動<br />\n目標一致 6.9 反送中<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>勿忘初心</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>溫馨提示</strong></span></span><br />\n如果 真係發生佔領 到時該區附近應急物資可能會短缺<br />\n希望各區人士 唔留守嘅都好 有時間方便嘅 <br />\n係各區買物資帶過去<br />\n<br />\n上次旺角無哂生理鹽水 全部藥房無貨<br />\n我住果區距離旺角比較遠 藥房有大量貨<br />\n可以買出去出面放底支援</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"94db39fd364db52a403b48608b158e80e73a9472","tid":1191833,"uid":58266,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:11:25.000Z","msg":"終於有個良心post。我都贊成要出來行，但係行到要出位就無謂。講真今次送中如果無有錢佬係後面推波助瀾唔會有咁的聲勢。我唔係話敵人的敵人就係朋友（地產霸權），但係適可而止唔好被人順便利用到盡就得。"},{"pid":"61b2ea8ceb5649dff66eda5279170824e55acd0b","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:24:56.000Z","msg":"班無恥之徒唔理後果洗腦到d人以為呢個時刻犯法就係型、無錯。<br />\n<br />\n到真係衰左單大獲野，<br />\n判十碌八碌，甚至幾十碌，<br />\n你班人會唔會&quot;不散&quot;地照顧人地父母/老婆仔女?<br />\n<br />\n除左教人被拘捕後程序要點做，點同律師contact之外，仲為佢地做到d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係無啊。連登烈士援助基金呢? 到時有無人會夾錢呀?<br />\n最多都係返黎連登為佢地戴上&quot;烈士&quot;光環，<br />\n除左咁之外，實際上班無恥之徒都只係當佢地係用完即棄既爛頭卒。<br />\n<br />\n輕輕拋句: 佢死佢事，咁大個人應該識諗後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c10bfb7bcd9835a4bf9e64fdc3d876a62010d1","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"連登良心推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571a6d962b19244dc9c26a3d22ea1623e4ddc2b7","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8404963242b4fde467214e9e44d49b2ad3d4a8d","tid":1191833,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:21:22.000Z","msg":"連登良心推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141280b04fef353c0096a8f9ae8cf68b23072c6a","tid":1191833,"uid":61498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:54:07.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n連登仔會用鍵盤幫呢班人架麻"},{"pid":"b4d8244a013ecf987701113f80412a98fc766f0a","tid":1191833,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:43:00.000Z","msg":"如果人生只係得番錢 你既人品真係可憐得好緊要<br />\n依0.3送比你啦垃圾"},{"pid":"a143b57b790f1973168323b0e300